Replace the 'SourceTimestamp' value *from* the timestamp of the commit *to* the timestamp of the data upload to the performance DB.

When using the commit timestamp with multiple builds of the same commit sha upon a data uploads would replace the perf data resulting in one [latest] date point for the multiple builds. Using the timestamp of the data upload ensures a separate data-point for each perf run of multiple builds of an identical commit sha.

